    "name": "Cursed Baby",
    "steam_appid": 3320330,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320330/extras/dd2e8f7f4733a7fe364cc35e1290f159.webp?t=1746014370\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a repairman who has just found a job cleaning and repairing an old house. The house is large, and although many things are broken, with your extensive repair experience, the job seems relatively easy. However, as you gradually delve into the rooms of this house, starting to find those strange diaries, everything you see gradually exceeds your imagination: a despairing mother, a possessed father, and an unbanishable demon! What exactly happened to this family? Beware, it’s always watching you... from above.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>📢</i> <i>Repair the old house </i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your tools and repair or clean various rooms in this haunted house. Be careful; danger may lurk in every corner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320330/extras/92995b1c4c3f374a245ac52b9b837196.avif?t=1746014370\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320330/extras_big/92995b1c4c3f374a245ac52b9b837196.avif?t=1746014370 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>📢 An inescapable demon.</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The old house has long been vacated, yet blurry strange figures and horrific laughter in the corridor constantly remind you that you are not alone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320330/extras/9de1573ee647b925ba668ae7964c1ed4.avif?t=1746014370\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320330/extras_big/9de1573ee647b925ba668ae7964c1ed4.avif?t=1746014370 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>📢 What happened in the house?</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect diaries scattered throughout the house. Was the evil force that once resided here truly banished?&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320330/extras/7387108b75505c6973417ba310930a74.webp?t=1746014370\" width=616 height=50 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320330/extras/c50088a8afb78c60d372df84d404c34c.avif?t=1746014370\" width=616 height=203 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320330/extras/fbf6355895168c14b584951785bfe0c5.avif?t=1746014370\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p>",
